_sText: Records for this map can be seen here. Stop by my server @ 63.251.20.40:27015 to add your time to the list. Aoki ____ Bunnyhop map centered around monster jam and a lot of jokes that you may or may not understand. Difficulty is easy/medium; can be done on stock settings. Each bhop has a corresponding climb path, so this could be played on an climb server as well. Map is 40 mb; 20/20 on map and custom content. You may need to increase net_maxfilesize in your server.cfg to play this. monster jam ___________ MONSTER JAM RULES AND SO DOES THIS MAP BY THE TRANSITIVE PROPERTY OF JAMMING. ENJOY.
